15 hours ago, VaderExMachina said:

this issue with the n1 is just as bad with TantaresLV, since he changed the .craft files,his n1 now just loads the second stage and thats it.

please raidernick listen to us, you did a n1 stock craft file before,why not make it again? or at least make a RO one like delta wee said.

 

ummmmm there ARE ro craft files for all of my parts...i swear nobody looks for anything anymore....the ro github has the craft files.....

6 hours ago, raidernick said:

ummmmm there ARE ro craft files for all of my parts...i swear nobody looks for anything anymore....the ro github has the craft files.....

did check RO craft files....no N1 there either.

18 hours ago, wm1248 said:

For those looking for a craft file, here is how you can build the N1, then save it in the VAB as a craft file and voila, future usage availability. Took me less than 10 minutes to build it. 

Could you post your craft file of your N1 somewhere, maybe as pull request to the main Soviet Rockets github repo? Getting the staging right on big rockets like this is where most of the time is spent when I build them.

7 hours ago, raidernick said:

ummmmm there ARE ro craft files for all of my parts...i swear nobody looks for anything anymore....the ro github has the craft files.....

I did a search for "N1" here and didn't get any hits: https://github.com/KSP-RO/RealismOverhaul/tree/master/Ships/VAB

Is the craft file for the N1 called something else?
@raidernick you say RO has the .craft files,  i did check them and can guarantee you that there is NO n1 file there

20 hours ago, VaderExMachina said:

@raidernick you say RO has the .craft files,  i did check them and can guarantee you that there is NO n1 file there

And that`s not the problem of raidernick instead of the RO-guys. So ask them and not raidernick.

2 minutes ago, Cheesecake said:

And that`s not the problem of raidernick instead of the RO-guys. So ask them and not raidernick.

his mod, his problem, he added it to RO, then he should be who fixes it.

2 hours ago, VaderExMachina said:

his mod, his problem, he added it to RO, then he should be who fixes it.

Right, his mod. And when he says that there aren`t any craft-files in the download then it is his own decision. RO is not raidernicks mod and so he isn`t responsible for any content in RO. Adding craftfiles to RO is part of the RO-Team, not the modder of the part-mods.

5 hours ago, VaderExMachina said:

his mod, his problem, he added it to RO, then he should be who fixes it.

Where do you get off telling me what I should and should not do here? I don't owe you or anyone else here anything. I do this for free on my own time because I want to, if you have a problem with that, then that's just too bad.

Edited July 2, 2018 by raidernick
my apologies, didn't meant to be so rude.
A publicly accessible N1 craft file would increase the number of people who can have a hands-on experience of an N1 mission.
Fairing and block A are wrong shape

7 hours ago, Cheesecake said:

Do you use the right versions of this mod for KSP 1.3.1? The newest ones are for 1.4.x.

I used RN-Mods in 1.3.1 without any problems. It should be a problem of other mods.

I used the latest version, however, I specifically downloaded the one for KSP 1.3.1 . None of the other mods crash KSP when I remove RN-Mods. The only other mods I am using are realism overhaul recommended mods. I think I see what my problem may be: I used CKAN to install RO and RSS

Please, fix N1!!!

On 8/6/2018 at 11:29 AM, Marsianin said:

Please, fix N1!!!

Why fix it? It works.
Пожалуйсто, не останавливайся над работой!!! Твои моды лучшие из всех модов на советские и российские космические аппараты. Спасибо тебе за проделанную работу и с нетерпением ждем продолжения!!!!

02.07.2018 в 11:21, рейдерник сказал:

Куда ты собираешься сказать мне, что я должен и не должен делать здесь? Я никому не обязан вам или кому-либо еще. Я делаю это бесплатно в свое время, потому что я хочу, если у вас есть проблемы с этим, тогда это слишком плохо.

Лично я и мои друзья благодарны тебе за твою работу! Ждем еще твоих работ. 

 

ты не планировал сделать модули станции мир? Базовый блок, квант, квант1, спектр, природа, кристал?

Those are already done in the bobcat iss/mir packs. I'm not doing those as they were all flown after the end of the soviet union

Сегодня сравнил твой мод и bobcat. Разница очень большая. Твой мод лучше, красивее. Мир bobcat не соответствует размерам. Твой мод по всем параметрам лучше. Твой мод реалистичнее. Интереснее играть в твой мод. 

PS. Я водитель автобуса. Живу и работаю в России. Я увлекаюсь космосом и KSP. С уважением отношись к любым космическим аппаратам: Союз, Алмаз, Восток, Солют, Апполон, Спейслаб, Спейсшаттл. Для меня нет разницы США или СССР/Росиия. Важно что эти аппараты есть в игре KSP благодаря таким людям как ты. Огромное тебе за это спасибо) Буду следить за новостями и ждать новых модов.
